From: Ravi Bangoria <ravi.bangoria@amd.com>
Date: Tue, 10 Dec 2024 09:34:48 +0000
Subject: perf test: Introduce DEFINE_SUITE_EXCLUSIVE()
Git-commit: 4cd67bac9d4e50938516c3ca3fdcfc31a34cb8d0
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

A variant of DEFINE_SUITE() but sets ->exclusive bit for the test so the
test will be executed sequentially.

